[SPEAKER_00] jer, rekao sam na početku,

325
00:17:31,440 --> 00:17:32,539
[SPEAKER_00] njih je lakše presložiti.

326
00:17:32,539 --> 00:17:34,319
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, sve što se događa

327
00:17:34,319 --> 00:17:37,339
[SPEAKER_00] sa hrvatskim izvođačima

328
00:17:37,339 --> 00:17:38,220
[SPEAKER_00] se može presložiti

329
00:17:38,220 --> 00:17:39,140
[SPEAKER_00] u nekoliko tjedana.

330
00:17:39,140 --> 00:17:41,180
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ako neki veliki band

331
00:17:41,180 --> 00:17:42,299
[SPEAKER_00] ne ide na svjetsku turneju,

332
00:17:42,299 --> 00:17:43,700
[SPEAKER_00] onda vi njega jednostavno nemate.

333
00:17:43,700 --> 00:17:44,400
[SPEAKER_00] To će biti ključno.

334
00:17:44,400 --> 00:17:46,160
[SPEAKER_01] Kako će se izvođači zapravo ponašati,

335
00:17:46,160 --> 00:17:47,299
[SPEAKER_01] kako će organizirati turneje,

336
00:17:48,420 --> 00:17:49,400
[SPEAKER_01] šta gdje će stići,

337
00:17:49,400 --> 00:17:50,359
[SPEAKER_01] jer u biti odjednom

338
00:17:50,359 --> 00:17:51,539
[SPEAKER_01] će biti ogromno potraženje za njima.

339
00:17:51,539 --> 00:17:53,160
[SPEAKER_01] Neće ni oni moći se zapravo

340
00:17:53,160 --> 00:17:53,920
[SPEAKER_01] klonirati okolo.

341
00:17:53,920 --> 00:17:54,539
[SPEAKER_00] Mi si jednostavno.

342
00:17:54,539 --> 00:17:55,740
[SPEAKER_00] Najmo zamisliti u ovom trenutku

343
00:17:55,740 --> 00:17:57,640
[SPEAKER_00] kako izgleda svjetska turneja

344
00:17:57,640 --> 00:17:58,619
[SPEAKER_00] redko chili peppersa.

345
00:17:58,619 --> 00:18:00,619
[SPEAKER_00] Convoj šlepara,

346
00:18:00,619 --> 00:18:02,700
[SPEAKER_00] dva, tri aviona,

347
00:18:02,700 --> 00:18:03,880
[SPEAKER_00] ogromna logistika.

348
00:18:03,880 --> 00:18:06,400
[SPEAKER_00] Da li je to moglo?

349
00:18:06,400 --> 00:18:07,859
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to je jednako

350
00:18:07,859 --> 00:18:09,539
[SPEAKER_00] komplicirano kao Formula 1

351
00:18:09,539 --> 00:18:10,160
[SPEAKER_00] koja ove godine

352
00:18:10,160 --> 00:18:10,920
[SPEAKER_00] još se nije usudila

353
00:18:10,920 --> 00:18:11,759
[SPEAKER_00] izaći iz Evropi.

354
00:18:11,759 --> 00:18:14,140
[SPEAKER_02] A koliko si ti, Bero,

355
00:18:14,140 --> 00:18:15,160
[SPEAKER_02] odnosno koliko ste vi

356
00:18:15,160 --> 00:18:17,380
[SPEAKER_02] u entry-u morali vratiti ulaznica?

357
00:18:17,380 --> 00:18:19,140
[SPEAKER_02] Koliko je ljudi vjerovalo

358
00:18:19,140 --> 00:18:20,500
[SPEAKER_02] da će se ponovo

359
00:18:20,500 --> 00:18:21,640
[SPEAKER_02] u tom trenutku

360
00:18:21,640 --> 00:18:23,440
[SPEAKER_02] festivali održavati,

361
00:18:23,440 --> 00:18:24,660
[SPEAKER_02] a koliko je tražilo povrat?

362
00:18:24,660 --> 00:18:25,740
[SPEAKER_02] Je li bio to veliki projek?

363
00:18:26,200 --> 00:18:27,099
[SPEAKER_01] Gledam, znači,

364
00:18:27,099 --> 00:18:28,039
[SPEAKER_01] ono što je zanimljivo

365
00:18:28,039 --> 00:18:28,799
[SPEAKER_01] svi nas pitaju kao,

366
00:18:28,799 --> 00:18:30,500
[SPEAKER_01] okej, ha, ljeto nije bilo posla,

367
00:18:30,500 --> 00:18:32,500
[SPEAKER_01] kao ono, bili ste na holdu.

368
00:18:32,500 --> 00:18:33,359
[SPEAKER_01] Ne da smo bili na holdu,

369
00:18:33,359 --> 00:18:34,720
[SPEAKER_01] nego smo radili tri puta više

370
00:18:34,720 --> 00:18:35,759
[SPEAKER_01] nego što radimo inače

371
00:18:35,759 --> 00:18:37,039
[SPEAKER_01] za nula prihoda,

372
00:18:37,039 --> 00:18:38,579
[SPEAKER_01] zato što upravo to obrađivali smo

373
00:18:38,579 --> 00:18:39,220
[SPEAKER_01] na fondacije,

374
00:18:39,220 --> 00:18:40,119
[SPEAKER_01] radili smo povrate.

375
00:18:40,119 --> 00:18:41,480
[SPEAKER_01] Istina je bitno za napomem

376
00:18:41,480 --> 00:18:42,259
[SPEAKER_01] da smo cijelo vrijeme

377
00:18:42,259 --> 00:18:42,980
[SPEAKER_01] radili povrate,

378
00:18:42,980 --> 00:18:44,240
[SPEAKER_01] naravno, doguru s organizatorima.

379
00:18:44,240 --> 00:18:44,960
[SPEAKER_01] Cijelo vrijeme smo radili

380
00:18:44,960 --> 00:18:45,940
[SPEAKER_01] isplato u organizatorima,

381
00:18:45,940 --> 00:18:46,599
[SPEAKER_01] dok znamo da,

382
00:18:46,599 --> 00:18:48,019
[SPEAKER_01] ovoga, jedan dobar dio

383
00:18:48,019 --> 00:18:49,980
[SPEAKER_01] i lokalne i globalne konkurencije,

384
00:18:49,980 --> 00:18:50,700
[SPEAKER_01] to nije radio

385
00:18:50,700 --> 00:18:52,019
[SPEAKER_01] i zadržavuje novce kod sebe,

386
00:18:52,019 --> 00:18:53,079
[SPEAKER_01] imali, bili su probleme,

387
00:18:53,079 --> 00:18:53,700
[SPEAKER_01] a mi smo cijelo vrijeme

388
00:18:53,700 --> 00:18:54,400
[SPEAKER_01] to isplačivali,

389
00:18:54,400 --> 00:18:56,059
[SPEAKER_01] ali što se tiče povrata,

390
00:18:56,059 --> 00:18:57,539
[SPEAKER_01] ako pričamo o festivalima,

391
00:18:57,539 --> 00:19:00,180
[SPEAKER_01] veći dio ljudi je zadržao ulaznice

392
